{"tid":2024981,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"王喜扮警察 網上辱垃圾","createTime":"2020-05-20T03:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T03:58:55.000Z","uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8efa32c675268e6b4e214c9656ec103c12a734ee","tid":2024981,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"尋日仲見到有個post話王喜死機佬之類 <br />\n你講咩春阿<br />\n王喜先係受害者<br />\n<blockquote>通訊局亦留意到節目內「驚方訊息」環節，主持人裝扮成警務人員並以廢物膠袋裹着頸項和雙手，開場時從大型垃圾桶冒出，環節完結時退回大型垃圾桶，其後六集均有類似描繪。通訊局認為，一般觀眾都能明顯察覺到，該環節對警方惡意描繪，暗示警務人員被視為廢物，遭人厭惡唾棄。其後數集重複有關描述，顯示是有意圖持續宣揚當中隱含的侮辱和偏見。通訊局認為，儘管該節目為政治諷刺節目，但該環節主持的描繪，令整個警隊受到污衊和侮辱。</blockquote><br />\n尋日仲見到<br />\n#王喜扮警察 #網上辱垃圾"},{"pid":"0d3f5b8722455566061e11272e00949dfdf0996f","tid":2024981,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527084-20200519.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527084-20200519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=962faae0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527084-20200519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=91c59343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527084-20200519.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9c22cf402c0b17f39a5576d7715147daf282aab7","tid":2024981,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"王喜cosplay就係差佬？ <br />\n小豪子就係公公？<br />\n太后就係慈禧？<br />\n唔怪得是旦搵個人坐上位就係主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce75daf91e7e05f34bf7e7579517afa11a0ed05","tid":2024981,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:17:06.000Z","msg":"森爺&amp;志豪整合：<br />\n１）頭條新聞靈魂不再 就算再接力落去 只不過徒有各軀殼<br />\n。利用政府公帑　諷刺政府才有意味<br />\n。資金上　廠境人員佔節目影響質素　<br />\n。若遵